==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Reasonist
<hw>Rea"son*ist</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A rationalist.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Such persons are now commonly called
⟦ldquo⟧<qex>reasonists</qex>⟦rdquo⟧ and ⟦ldquo⟧rationalists,⟦rdquo⟧ to
distinguish them from true reasoners and rational inquirers.</q>
<rj><qau>Waterland.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Reasonless</ent>⟦br⟧
